Mahaut arranges for her daughter Jeanne to be released from her imprisonment at Dourdan so that she can continue to be the wife of the future Philippe V; Olenna arranges for her granddaughter Margaery to marry King Joffrey.
Mahaut has Louis X poisoned so that Philippe and Jeanne can be King and Queen; Olenna has Joffrey poisoned so that Margaery can marry the gentler and more malleable Tommen.
